name: Eagle Speedmapping Session 4 - Four Square!
description: The fourth Eagle Speedmapping Sessions' goal was to make maps within a 2 (in practice 3) hour limit. Five maps were made, and the themes were: - No possesed humans - 1024x1024 playable area limit - No ammo except berserk Plus a bonus theme for the chaps (everyone) who showed up for the final round: - Map must be centered around lava!
